BILLIONTON SYSTE said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 50.12% to NT$18,234,000 from NT$36,554,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             18,234           36,554    
YOY%             -50.12%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             68,787          123,371    
YOY%             -44.24% 
=================================================================
 